raw.name: #1 Drama (M4)
raw.bio: Good morning, I'm #1 Drama (M4), but what's in a name, anyway? My parents fed me ranch dressing when I was a kid and I refuse to eat it now. Peace out!

raw.name: Dieter Tickdork
raw.bio: How goes it. My name is Dieter Tickdork. I pretty much only listen to Blake Shelton. Every Tuesday evening I watch tv and binge on salt water taffy. It makes the rest of the week bearable. Would you believe that Diane Keaton is just like you and me?

raw.name: Floyd Lackapuss
raw.bio: Hello. I'm Floyd Lackapuss, you may know me from The Graduate. I always thought I'd be a great Brand Consultant, except I'm not fragrant enough. Someday, all of this will be yours.

raw.name: #1 Liger (M4)
raw.bio: Yikes! You scared me. My name is #1 Liger (M4), and my game is siring for status. I combine the best qualities of Rose McGowan, Abraham Lincoln, and Mozart. I want to know what love is. I want you to show me.

raw.name: Nana Meanbutt
raw.bio: Guten tag. I like picking daisies because my name is Nana Meanbutt. I heard a rumour Shia LaBeouf was running for president. They'd have my vote. Come, I'll show you my collection of ketchup.

raw.name: Precious Bobopants
raw.bio: Greetings. I'm Precious Bobopants. I can tell we're going to have a good time together. My new life goal is to catch a faun and make it share its powers with me. Get ready to lie in the sun and do nothing all day with me.

raw.name: Boots Meowpet
raw.bio: Yikes! You scared me. I'm Boots Meowpet, your new best fur-end. I would go on a date with a octopus just to interview Barbara Walters. I find corn dogs make me sneeze.

raw.name: Willing to Consider Offers!
raw.bio: Hi, I'm Willing to Consider Offers!. And you are? Imagine me as Sir John A. MacDonald's more smelly sibling. I'm going to show you the time of your life.

raw.name: King Khanson
raw.bio: *hissing noises*. I'm King Khanson, and I will do almost anything to star in a soap opera. All I want in life is to listen to my Katy Perry CDs in peace. Is that too much to ask? Gahhh, aren't you cute!
